            h2 Popular YT Performances
            img.croppedPhoto(src='../site/img/youtubeHIT.jpg' alt='youtubeHIT' align='right' style='width: 280px; height: auto')
            p.textwrap Party in the USA was just the beginning as Christina kept honing her talents and becoming a minor celebrity in the YouTube community.  Most of her releases reached view count of more than a million per video.  Christina was just getting started!
