            h2 Road to Stardom
            img.croppedPhoto(src='../site/img/cyrusMedley.jpg' alt='youtubecompetition' align='right' style='width: 290px; height: auto')
            p.textwrap As Christina's fan base and subscription to her channel kept growing, she gained more recognition for her vocal talents.  She was noticed by Selena Gomez's stepfather, Brian Teefey, who became interested in Christina's talents after watching several performance.  Around the time after Christina's performance of 'Miley Cyrus Medley' produced by Kurt Hugo Schneider, Brian Teefey contacted Grimmie and became her manager.
            a.icon(title='https://www.youtube.com/embed/Ua4EESKuCAs' href='') Miley Cyrus Medley
            span.cd-date
          // cd-timeline-content
        // cd-timeline-block
