            h2 The Voice 2014
            img.croppedPhoto(src='../site/img/thevoice.jpg' alt='thevoice' align='right' style='width: 290px; height: auto')
            p.textwrap During the 2014 "The Voice" competition, Grimmie auditioned for a spot by singing Miley Cyrus' "Wrecking Ball" where all four coaches, immediately, approved and turned around to receive her.  She was hotly contested after by the coaches and Grimmie eventually decided to go with Adam Levine as her coach.  She placed 3rd in the competition behind Josh Kaufman (winner) and Jake Worthington (runner-up).
            a.icon(title='https://www.youtube.com/embed/zTIfBXxgfrk' href='') The Voice - Miley Cyrus' Wrecking Ball
            br
            a.icon(title='https://www.youtube.com/embed/y-FDy03JxVc?list=PLRTt-MZzzTAZBPc69-7chIgFOYJYUFXQI' href='') The Voice - All Performances
            span.cd-date
