            h2 iHeartRadio
            h2 Third Single: "Shrug"
            img.croppedPhoto(src='../site/img/iheartradio2.jpg' alt='iheartradio' align='right' style='width: 290px; height: auto')
            p.textwrap While receiving moderate success from her newly released singles, Grimmie was also entered into the iHeartRadio/Macy's "Rising Star" contest which was designed to support unsigned/independent musicians/artists and will be featured across the nation over hundreds of radio stations.  The winner of the contest will also have the honor of performing at the iHeartRadio Music Festival in Las Vegas.  On May 27, 2015, Grimmie published on YouTube to announce and record her reaction to the news that she won the iHeartRadio/Macy's contest.  Her third single of the year, "Shrug" was released in the summer, July 2nd.
            a.icon(title='https://www.youtube.com/embed/SVpjedp89IQ' href='') Grimmie Wins iHeartRadio Contest
